{
  "texts": [
    "We acknowledge that the choice of annotators could have induced a level of subjective interpretation.",
    "However, the random selection and shuffling of segments for annotation likely mitigated any subconscious biases.",
    "Moreover, the high inter-rater reliability indicates that the suggestions provided were clear and consistent, regardless of the annotators' prior involvement in the process.",
    "The online part of the pipeline consists of retrieving a tailored comparison recipe for the user in real-time.",
    "Quality Prediction."
  ]
}